title: [Garden of Making]
description: Shaded by the willowy bulks of linden trees, the enclosed glade is dark and choked with primal greenery.  Mimicking the rising trees, a series of spiraling metal constructs rises from the verdant earth, forming a rough circle that guards the stunted form of a thriving faewood tree.
